## Section 1 — Inscriptions & Dossiers (row)

**Panel 1.1 — Flux dossiers en temps réel** (logs)
```
... | action=~"DOSSIER_CREE|DOSSIER_RETENU|DOSSIER_REJETE|DOSSIER_ANNULE_EXPIRATION|DOSSIER_ANNULE_VOLONTAIRE|PAIEMENT_VOUCHER_ORG_CONFIRME"
| line_format "{{.action}} — dossier={{.metadata_dossier_id}} statut={{.metadata_statut}}"
```

**Panel 1.2 — Dossiers créés / 5m** (timeseries)
```
sum(rate(... | action="DOSSIER_CREE" [5m]))
```

**Panel 1.3 — Pipeline dossiers par statut / 1h** (bar chart, sum by action)
```
sum by (action) (count_over_time(... | action=~"DOSSIER_CREE|DOSSIER_RETENU|DOSSIER_REJETE|DOSSIER_ANNULE_EXPIRATION|DOSSIER_ANNULE_VOLONTAIRE" [1h]))
```

**Panel 1.4 — Dossiers expirés** (logs)
```
... | action="DOSSIER_ANNULE_EXPIRATION"
| line_format "EXPIRE — dossier={{.metadata_dossier_id}} motif={{.metadata_motif}}"
```

---

## Section 2 — Paiements (row)

**Panel 2.1 — Flux paiements en temps réel** (logs)
```
... | action=~"IPN_SUCCESS_TRAITE|IPN_FAIL_TRAITE|FINEO_CB_SUCCESS_TRAITE|FINEO_CB_FAIL_TRAITE|PAIEMENT_INITIE|IPN_MONTANT_MISMATCH|PAIEMENT_MONTANT_MISMATCH"
| line_format "{{.action}} — paiement={{.metadata_paiement_id}} dossier={{.metadata_dossier_id}}"
```

**Panel 2.2 — Succès vs Échecs paiements / 5m** (timeseries, 2 séries)
```
# Succès
sum(rate(... | action=~"IPN_SUCCESS_TRAITE|FINEO_CB_SUCCESS_TRAITE" [5m]))
# Échecs
sum(rate(... | action=~"IPN_FAIL_TRAITE|FINEO_CB_FAIL_TRAITE" [5m]))
```

**Panel 2.3 — Anomalies paiement** (logs, fond rouge)
```
... | action=~"IPN_MONTANT_MISMATCH|FINEO_CB_MONTANT_MISMATCH|PAIEMENT_MONTANT_MISMATCH|IPN_MOVED_TO_DLQ_REDIS|IPN_PAIEMENT_INTROUVABLE"
```

**Panel 2.4 — Abonnements activés / échoués** (logs)
```
... | action=~"IPN_ABONNEMENT_ACTIVE|IPN_ABONNEMENT_ECHEC|IPN_ABONNEMENT_ORG_ACTIVE|IPN_ABONNEMENT_ORG_ECHEC|IPN_ABONNEMENT_B2B_ACTIVE|IPN_ABONNEMENT_B2B_ECHEC"
| line_format "{{.action}} — id={{.metadata_abonnement_id}}"
```

