## Section 4 — Activité plateforme (row)

**Panel 4.1 — Formations & Vouchers** (logs)
```
... | action=~"FORMATION_CREEE|FORMATION_PARTENAIRE_VALIDEE|FORMATION_PARTENAIRE_REJETEE|VOUCHER_ORGANISATION_CREE|VOUCHER_PROMOTIONNEL_VALIDE|DEVIS_CREE|DEVIS_PAYE"
| line_format "{{.action}} {{.timestamp}}"
```

**Panel 4.2 — Sessions (transitions automatiques)** (logs)
```
... | action=~"SESSION_CREEE|SESSION_CLOTUREE|SESSION_ANNULEE|SESSION_TRANSITION_AUTO"
| line_format "{{.action}} — session={{.metadata_session_id}} {{.metadata_ancien_statut}}→{{.metadata_nouveau_statut}}"
```

**Panel 4.3 — Schedulers — dernières exécutions** (logs)
```
... | action=~"RECONCILIATION_NGSER_FIN|DOSSIER_ANNULE_EXPIRATION|SESSION_TRANSITION_AUTO|COMMISSIONS_AGREGEES|ALERTES_FIN_ESSAI_ORGANISATION"
```

**Panel 4.4 — Activité globale / 5m** (timeseries, sum by action, top actions métier)
```
sum by (action) (count_over_time(... | action=~"DOSSIER_CREE|IPN_SUCCESS_TRAITE|IPN_FAIL_TRAITE|COMMISSION_APPORTEUR_CREEE|SESSION_CREEE|VOUCHER_ORGANISATION_CREE" [5m]))
```

